noExcessiveCognitiveComplexity.option:
Allows specifying the maximum allowed complexity.
{  "linter": {    "rules": {      "complexity": {        "noExcessiveCognitiveComplexity": {          "options": {            "maxAllowedComplexity":           }        }      }    }  }}
The allowed values range from 1 through 254. The default is 15.
